    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "gsi2_content",
      "x": 522, "y": 722,
      "width": 446, "height": 168,
      "text": "Vet → Bookings (by status):\n  GSI2PK=VET#vetId\n  GSI2SK begins_with BOOKING#upcoming#\n\nVet → Assessments (pending queue):\n  GSI2PK=VET#vetId\n  GSI2SK begins_with ASSESSMENT#pending#\n\nVet → Threads (open only):\n  GSI2PK=VET#vetId\n  GSI2SK begins_with THREAD#open#",
      "originalText": "Vet → Bookings (by status):\n  GSI2PK=VET#vetId\n  GSI2SK begins_with BOOKING#upcoming#\n\nVet → Assessments (pending queue):\n  GSI2PK=VET#vetId\n  GSI2SK begins_with ASSESSMENT#pending#\n\nVet → Threads (open only):\n  GSI2PK=VET#vetId\n  GSI2SK begins_with THREAD#open#",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
