    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "gsi3_content",
      "x": 1012, "y": 722,
      "width": 536, "height": 168,
      "text": "List vets/behaviourists by type, sorted by rating:\n  GSI3PK=PROVIDER_TYPE#behaviourist\n  GSI3SK begins_with RATING#\n\nKey design: RATING#4.9#VET#uuid\n  → GSI returns vets sorted highest-rated first\n  → No post-query sort operation\n  → 4.7 < 4.9 < 5.0 sorts correctly as string\n\nAlt (rating as attribute, sort client-side):\n  Must read ALL vets + O(n) in-memory sort",
      "originalText": "List vets/behaviourists by type, sorted by rating:\n  GSI3PK=PROVIDER_TYPE#behaviourist\n  GSI3SK begins_with RATING#\n\nKey design: RATING#4.9#VET#uuid\n  → GSI returns vets sorted highest-rated first\n  → No post-query sort operation\n  → 4.7 < 4.9 < 5.0 sorts correctly as string\n\nAlt (rating as attribute, sort client-side):\n  Must read ALL vets + O(n) in-memory sort",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
