    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dd1_content",
      "x": 32, "y": 988,
      "width": 346, "height": 150,
      "text": "SK: BOOKING#upcoming#2026-04-18T10:00\n\nQuery: SK begins_with BOOKING#upcoming#\n→ Returns ONLY upcoming bookings\n\nWithout this: FilterExpression on status\n→ Reads ALL bookings (upcoming + completed\n  + cancelled) then filters in memory\n→ Wastes RCUs on every discarded row",
      "originalText": "SK: BOOKING#upcoming#2026-04-18T10:00\n\nQuery: SK begins_with BOOKING#upcoming#\n→ Returns ONLY upcoming bookings\n\nWithout this: FilterExpression on status\n→ Reads ALL bookings (upcoming + completed\n  + cancelled) then filters in memory\n→ Wastes RCUs on every discarded row",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#94a3b8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
