    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dd2_content",
      "x": 418, "y": 988,
      "width": 346, "height": 150,
      "text": "Thread:  PK=THREAD#abc  SK=METADATA\nMessage: PK=THREAD#abc  SK=MSG#time#id\n\nQuery(PK=THREAD#abc, SK begins_with MSG#)\n→ ALL messages in 1 call. Zero joins.\n\nAlternative (separate PK per message):\n→ 2+ calls needed: fetch thread, then messages\n→ Higher cost, more failure surface,\n  no guaranteed ordering",
      "originalText": "Thread:  PK=THREAD#abc  SK=METADATA\nMessage: PK=THREAD#abc  SK=MSG#time#id\n\nQuery(PK=THREAD#abc, SK begins_with MSG#)\n→ ALL messages in 1 call. Zero joins.\n\nAlternative (separate PK per message):\n→ 2+ calls needed: fetch thread, then messages\n→ Higher cost, more failure surface,\n  no guaranteed ordering",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#94a3b8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 650007,
