    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dd4_content",
      "x": 1190, "y": 988,
      "width": 358, "height": 150,
      "text": "GSI3SK: RATING#4.7#VET#uuid-a\n         RATING#4.9#VET#uuid-b\n         RATING#5.0#VET#uuid-c\n\nGSI Query returns vets sorted by rating.\nZero post-query sort. Free ordered listing.\n\nAlternative (sort client-side):\n→ Read ALL vets for the provider type\n→ O(n) in-memory sort\n→ Full scan, not pageable by rating",
      "originalText": "GSI3SK: RATING#4.7#VET#uuid-a\n         RATING#4.9#VET#uuid-b\n         RATING#5.0#VET#uuid-c\n\nGSI Query returns vets sorted by rating.\nZero post-query sort. Free ordered listing.\n\nAlternative (sort client-side):\n→ Read ALL vets for the provider type\n→ O(n) in-memory sort\n→ Full scan, not pageable by rating",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#94a3b8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
